tvinfomerk2vdr-ng/USAGE
=======================

Prerequisites:
--------------
- installation
- configuration


Usage:
------

One-Time run in test mode (not applying any action) for "tvinfo" (default)

./tvinfomerk2vdr-ng.pl -U <service-user> -P <service-pass> -N


One-Time run in test mode (not applying any action) for "tvdirekt"

./tvinfomerk2vdr-ng.pl -U <service-user> -P <service-pass> --service tvdirekt -N
